						<td rowspan=2 bgcolor="#0C142B" width=1><img src="/i/p.gif" height=1 width=1 border=0 alt=""><br></td>
			<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; " >
												<DIV>Seeing how bard lulls cap at the same level as monk, enchanter, cleric, and other class lulls I don't see that being the problem.&nbsp; Bards and enchanters both are capped at the highest level of 68 for mez, so anything that renders our mezzes useless renders mezzes across the board useless.&nbsp; If mez, lull, and snare just absolutely won't work on a group of mobs, the only methods of pulling would be using FD or judicious use of Fading Memories.&nbsp; I don't see a problem with that--it's just a change in challenge.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>As far as post ikkinz, bards do phenomenally well.&nbsp; I've gotten as far as Inktu'ta and am having no problems pulling, CC'ing, or proving my use to a group or raid.&nbsp; I've single pulled/CC'ed/slowed all of Qvic for a small raid with very few problems and provided backup CC for raids in Qvic and Inktu'ta.&nbsp; That's not to mention the AE resists, Dark Echo, and other defensive songs in all of these zones.&nbsp; I used Dark Echo a TON in Uqua and Inktu'ta to curb a lot of damage from my group and add a little damage here and there.&nbsp; Without resists via AE songs and psalms the raid would be hurting.&nbsp; I can't say much about post Inktu'ta, but life without bards would be hard I would imagine.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>In general if we can't pull/CC at all, neither can most of the other classes we share those roles with (except maybe monks, but even then Fading Memories has applications that allow us to work with them to pull).&nbsp; </DIV>
																																		<p><div style="width: 100%; height: 100; overflow: hidden;">
														<p>-<a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=994568>Sedenten Grey</a><br>Maestro of Firiona Vie<br><a href=http://www.fnfguild.com>Fire and Fury</a><br><br>-<a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=222062>Booperbustle Tinkermeister</a><br>Arch Convoker of Solusek Ro<br><a href=http://www.furiouspantaloons.org>Furious Pantaloons</a>
